mdhn:RE_38v a mdhn:RegisterEntry;
    rdfs:label "The Court of Faridun, his mother Faranak sends gifts to her son"@en, "ارسال هدايا از سوی فرانک به پسران فريدون"@fa;
    rdfs:comment "When the news of Faridun's enthronement spreads, his mother, Faranak, sends Arabian horses, gold, gems, and other gifts. Notables the world over offer gifts and journey to pay homage to the new king."@en;
